{
  "stem": "1222.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were so hard knocking that when we slept in the police station, we were scared to come sleep anywhere, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The windows were slotted out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was bombs, everything there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I figured we're not going away no place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because if they have to run back, we'll run with the partisans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were good ammunition and everything there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then after, they arrested a lot of Ukrainian people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know what they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But there they sent them to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because they were taking it-- and they did not play around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Mine friend, he was so bitter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "When he used to go around in the basement when the police didn't check him, he used to have a small little knife, very, very sharp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he used to cut the meat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He used to say like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, Monek-- later on they didn't let him-- why are you cutting so badly?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, I want to see them bleeding like they bleed my parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I feel good when I see their blood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And up till today, he was scared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we were over there, he was scared in Miedzyrzecz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He went with me, by the way, in that thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was scared some Ukrainian will kill him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But unfortunately, he's still scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because if somebody would recognize him-- he's a redheaded one-- he would be in trouble.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They wouldn't touch me [INAUDIBLE], because I wasn't in-- mind you, I'm not hiding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I haven't got the heart to do this kind of stuff, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After that-- we-- should I continue that way?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Let me go back over a couple of things if you could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Let's--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
